.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, white, blood-red, light-blue
There are 4 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, italian
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, mouse
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
 2. the egyptian is the person who likes blood-red##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 4. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the person drinking juice is the person who likes light-blue##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the owner of the dog is the italian##1
 8. the person who likes light-blue is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the british##1
10. the owner of the dog is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | sprite    | juice      |
| Color           | blood-red | mauve | white | light-blue     |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | italian   | british   | indonesian |
| Pet           | mouse         | dog       | hedgehog  | goat       |

